name: Rome Outdoor Sofa
description: Get a comfortable place to enjoy the open air and transform your terrace into a contemporary living space with Rome. The minimal design, in high quality materials developed for all weather, ensures many years of great time in the sun. Use this open end module to add storage, decoration or a place to put down the coffee cup. The table section can be positioned on both sides of the module making it perfect as an end to your sofa combination or to stand alone as a lounge chair.
